        <h1>Outstanding Web Designs</h1>
        <p>This document contains an analysis of four web design projects selected from award nominees and winners, highlighting why they are considered outstanding examples of modern web design.</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="project1">
            <h2>Because Recollection</h2>
            <p><strong>Award:</strong> Awwwards</p>
            <p><strong>URL:</strong> <a href="http://www.because-recollection.com/" target="_blank">Visit Because Recollection</a></p>
            <p><strong>Analysis:</strong> 
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Interactive navigation:</strong> One of the standout features is the unique user interaction. Instead of traditional click-based navigation, users are invited to press the spacebar to change artists, creating a more engaging and immersive experience.</li>
                    <li><strong>Sound integration:</strong> The website makes brilliant use of sound, where the audio dynamically changes based on user actions. This interplay between navigation and sound elevates the experience, making the user feel more connected to the content.</li>
                    <li><strong>Animations and 2D/3D elements:</strong> The use of both 2D and 3D animations adds depth to the site, these visual layers create an immersive atmosphere, blending design, sound, and interaction seamlessly.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="image-grid">
