        <section id="project2">
            <h2>Why are we (not) creative?</h2>
            <p><strong>Award:</strong> Webby Awards</p>
            <p><strong>URL:</strong> <a href="https://whyarewecreative.com/en" target="_blank">Visit Why are we (not) creative?</a></p>
            <p><strong>Analysis:</strong>  
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Scrolling mechanics:</strong> The website stands out for its innovative use of scrolling. Instead of simply moving up or down, the site uses two containers—one scrolling normally and the other inverted. This hijacking of the scroll mechanic creates the sensation of switching between two worlds.</li>
                <li><strong>Color palette:</strong> The thoughtful use of color enhances the idea of transitioning between worlds.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="image-grid">
                <div class="image-container">
                <a href="https://whyarewecreative.com/en" target="_blank">
