        <section id="project3">
            <h2>Studio Gruhl</h2>
            <p><strong>Award:</strong> FWA </p>
            <p><strong>URL:</strong> <a href="https://www.studiogruhl.com/" target="_blank">Visit Studio Gruhl</a></p>
            <p><strong>Analysis:</strong>  
                <ul>
                <li><strong>Idle interaction:</strong> One of the standout features of this website is how the interface transforms when the user remains inactive. The melting effect that appears across the screen creates a psychedelic vibe, adding a sense of motion and creativity even when the user is not interacting with the page.</li>
                <li><strong>Mouse cursor design:</strong>The site’s cursor design is another notable element. The white circular mouse pointer that changes to black depending on the background underneath it offers a subtle but effective interactive touch, keeping the user visually engaged throughout the browsing experience.</li>
                <li><strong>Use of videos:</strong>  The website utilizes videos to present products, which adds depth and movement to the presentation. This approach not only captures attention but also makes the products feel more dynamic and immersive.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="image-grid">
                <div class="image-container">
